# ============================================================================
# NOTES
# ============================================================================

# This .gitignore is configured for maximum security.
# Key principles:
# 1. NEVER commit secrets (env vars, keystores, API keys)
# 2. NEVER commit build artifacts (APKs, AABs)
# 3. DO commit ProGuard mapping files (for crash reporting)
# 4. Keep it simple - add only what you need
